{"tid":84153,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過內蒙古？","createTime":"2017-01-17T10:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T17:09:35.000Z","uid":71422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf6df757aecd5b60f2fb7fac9e96fcb170e259a","tid":84153,"uid":71422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"通常旅行都係去日韓台<br />\n依家想去啲特別啲既地方<br />\n個人好中意睇風景<br />\n所以想去內蒙古<br />\n淨係知內蒙古有羊食<br />\n有動物睇<br />\n<br />\n有冇人去過內蒙古可以比啲意見？<br />\n想知果到治安好唔好？<br />\n應該自由行定跟團好玩啲？<br />\n洗費大概用左幾多？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e9976ad16fbd5f8502cd16291777987c8e3f49","tid":84153,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常旅行都係去日韓台<br />\n依家想去啲特別啲既地方<br />\n個人好中意睇風景<br />\n所以想去內蒙古<br />\n淨係知內蒙古有羊食<br />\n有動物睇<br />\n<br />\n有冇人去過內蒙古可以比啲意見？<br />\n想知果到治安好唔好？<br />\n應該自由行定跟團好玩啲？<br />\n洗費大概用左幾多？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內蒙啲囡囡都幾靚同好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c2be56b58afd4ae4ca75dff8636147bad61c44","tid":84153,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"二三線城市，d 女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次三月想去睇大草原，屌拿聲一條草都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD 導遊話七月到先多草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次跟圑北京出發5日4 夜 $699 人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bd24cb8e13325dbebc8bcd95d2e2ba15a22915","tid":84153,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"去過 呼和告特 唔好意爲大草園 難地就有。要去不如睇下外蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d70baf8f3d5102314222002ecadd71ee757c3e7","tid":84153,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"N 年前火車去<br />\n<br />\n真係風吹草低見牛羊咁，個銀河日出日落靚到不得了"},{"pid":"2750e7ecab9affa6906d307717d3e78ba2292e7b","tid":84153,"uid":37605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"我去果個草原又無你地講咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且夜晚仲有流星睇，但就凍到仆街，<br />\n啲新式蒙古包仲要無熱水沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8247f948221ae0f75128f655233b5fda9f6ecb38","tid":84153,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"睇你去邊到<br />\n大草原就唔使諗 禿撚哂<br />\n沙漠就反而係幾靚<br />\n不過呢啲係內蒙古郊區<br />\n包頭 鄂爾多斯 呼和浩特 全部係大城市<br />\n勁多高樓大慶而且勁乾淨<br />\n內蒙係中國最有錢嘅省份<br />\n如果你想睇遊牧民族騎馬射箭就會令你失望啦"},{"pid":"dd8cc6eb8edb5a8626442119dafe3c8d82ed984f","tid":84153,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"去睇星 小心有密集恐懼症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee271382e5a3c318ad5e3bcc96aa31833ed9a7","tid":84153,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"呼和浩特就唔好諗住睇到草啦 同一般中國城市冇乜分別 附近既草原都已經沙漠化<br />\n<br />\n要睇既就再搭火車去錫林浩特/飛機去呼倫貝爾<br />\n<br />\n不過要七月先係內蒙既旅遊季節，個陣五月尾去錫林浩特好多景點都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕遠既去呼倫貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講個邊d草係keep得最好"},{"pid":"354894ffd93834258c1b36891d480bf1bf01d642","tid":84153,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去睇星 小心有密集恐懼症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇相 share"},{"pid":"6b58f11e34bf670150fc23d328ac68d3d26e5a4b","tid":84153,"uid":48235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呼和浩特就唔好諗住睇到草啦 同一般中國城市冇乜分別 附近既草原都已經沙漠化<br />\n<br />\n要睇既就再搭火車去錫林浩特/飛機去呼倫貝爾<br />\n<br />\n不過要七月先係內蒙既旅遊季節，個陣五月尾去錫林浩特好多景點都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕遠既去呼倫貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講個邊d草係keep得最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過呼和浩特，好商業化既草原，比當地人笑9我話呢邊冇野睇，要去就一定去呼倫貝爾"},{"pid":"29f95f3f3f24ab7de1bc360a73dfcd2783655c3a","tid":84153,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二三線城市，d 女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次三月想去睇大草原，屌拿聲一條草都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD 導遊話七月到先多草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次跟圑北京出發5日4 夜 $699 人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁平！係大陸報團？"},{"pid":"1f12f30ec38db4065a12a4f86bbec4560997e803","tid":84153,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣係北京報 (去哪兒)<br />\n之後佢個團四日三夜<br />\n去蒙古大草原同埋去沙漠騎駱駝<br />\n個景好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾值得去"},{"pid":"caa6ba7260e20ff3d8c2014c910f1f7b237e874e","tid":84153,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:26:09.000Z","msg":"去過包頭 響沙灣沙漠 勁撚靚<br />\n仲有唔記得咩青原（但冬天無草）<br />\n呼和浩特  日日食饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fe5476ee031c179811e642d617ca1f9c3738da","tid":84153,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過包頭 響沙灣沙漠 勁撚靚<br />\n仲有唔記得咩青原（但冬天無草）<br />\n呼和浩特  日日食饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲去埋成吉思汗墓<br />\n<br />\n屌你 唔會再去  冬天零下幾度坐左成4粒鐘 原來係去睇室外博物館<br />\n凍到仆街  我全程流鼻水  個鼻凍到痛"},{"pid":"6ec1e2c4eaaba5f42f3f2ddd7115fa45d32076a8","tid":84153,"uid":45461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:34:10.000Z","msg":"中學遊學團去過，好商業化，係草原住蒙古包但其實係石屎黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a582ffafc430d36d837e25934bdbe917f1169c","tid":84153,"uid":53118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"想住蒙古包 同 睇草原<br />\n咩月份最好同去邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8746dcbd9dbd25719adef480e443bb0bf9379f3","tid":84153,"uid":36598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呼和浩特就唔好諗住睇到草啦 同一般中國城市冇乜分別 附近既草原都已經沙漠化<br />\n<br />\n要睇既就再搭火車去錫林浩特/飛機去呼倫貝爾<br />\n<br />\n不過要七月先係內蒙既旅遊季節，個陣五月尾去錫林浩特好多景點都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕遠既去呼倫貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講個邊d草係keep得最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年七月同屋企人一家四口去呼倫貝爾 五日四夜包車連司機連景點門票同住宿 total萬六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeae8853e945199cb19a56703bcd8ae095448c9a","tid":84153,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呼和浩特就唔好諗住睇到草啦 同一般中國城市冇乜分別 附近既草原都已經沙漠化<br />\n<br />\n要睇既就再搭火車去錫林浩特/飛機去呼倫貝爾<br />\n<br />\n不過要七月先係內蒙既旅遊季節，個陣五月尾去錫林浩特好多景點都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕遠既去呼倫貝爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講個邊d草係keep得最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年七月同屋企人一家四口去呼倫貝爾 五日四夜包車連司機連景點門票同住宿 total萬六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個人萬六定四個人萬六？"},{"pid":"1f4e58e91bf806353393c9c61223bb1086309916","tid":84153,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:04:54.000Z","msg":"一定要去科爾沁旗"},{"pid":"126e4c029001f7fe6a4eb097420db03ba209e09e","tid":84153,"uid":70497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"去過蒙古國後，你會發覺內蒙實在太唔掂"},{"pid":"70409d9df74f2ab2f4eb96a262f2ba6087f931e8","tid":84153,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過蒙古國後，你會發覺內蒙實在太唔掂</blockquote><br />\n啱啱想講<br />\n去得內蒙不如去蒙古"},{"pid":"a148e05713afc9a9de978fe42ed652381c457941","tid":84153,"uid":21291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"治安不錯<br />\n蒙古人幾熱情同主動<br />\n會關心你著唔夠衫<br />\n<br />\n同南方人明顯唔同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上兩星期去完內蒙古，第二次去，上次係夏天<br />\n冬天好小遊客，因為太凍啦，最凍零下-38度<br />\n<br />\n冰天雪地+雪漠 草原<br />\n靚到不得了<br />\n<br />\n張相係根河影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/010958_19865dc6818e30e3e4d51189e54a0497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F010958_19865dc6818e30e3e4d51189e54a0497.jpg&h=2eb1e8f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b0751e933b577a66a4e1e6b4771a6e4fb4aa797","tid":84153,"uid":49754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T00:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過蒙古國後，你會發覺內蒙實在太唔掂</blockquote><br />\n未去已經覺唔掂，勁商業化<br />\n好彩之後去埋蒙古，真係靚到唔識形容"},{"pid":"41e0